section.teaser
  .container
    .lead.text-center.title-text
      h1 Keep your data safe in the cloud
      p CryFS encrypts your files, so you can safely store them anywhere. It works well together with cloud services like Dropbox, iCloud, OneDrive and others.
      p
        ' We are currently in development.
        br
        ' Get notified when it's ready!
        div style="margin-top: 20px;"
          =form_for InterestedUser.new, remote: true, html: {id: "interested_user_form_1", class: 'form form-inline'} do |f|
            .form-group
              .sr-only for="interested_user_form_1-inputEmail" Email Address:
              =f.email_field :email, id: 'interested_user_form_1-inputEmail', class: "form-control", placeholder: "Enter email", required: true
            =button_tag(type: 'submit', class: "btn btn-primary", style: "margin-left: 5px;") do ||
              ' Get Notified&nbsp;
              i.fa.fa-angle-double-right
            div
              .collapse.form-success.form-success-small Thank you. We'll get in touch.
              .collapse.form-error.form-error-small Invalid email address.
          javascript:
            window.setup_ajax_forms = window.setup_ajax_forms || [];
            window.setup_ajax_forms.push("#interested_user_form_1");

      / p
        a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg href="#" role="button" Learn more »

section.section-1
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-4.text-center
        i.fa.fa-check-circle-o.teaser-icon
        h2 Simple
        p CryFS is easy to setup and works with a lot of cloud storage providers. Encryption works transparently, that is, in your daily workflow you won't notice a difference to using (say) Dropbox directly.
        p
          a.btn.btn-default href="#" role="button" View details »
      .col-md-4.text-center
        i.fa.fa-lock.teaser-icon
        h2 Secure
        p Every bit of data leaving your computer will be encrypted. CryFS never gives unencrypted data to the cloud. Not only file contents, but also file metadata and directory structure is encrypted. CryFS also protects you from someone modifying your data without your noticing.
        p
          a.btn.btn-default href="#" role="button" View details »
      .col-md-4.text-center
        i.fa.fa-diamond.teaser-icon-smaller
        h2 Free and Open Source
        p
          ' CryFS is released under LGPL and available on
          a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/smessmer/cryfs" github
          '. Everyone can look at the source code and check that it fulfills the given security promises. If you want, you can take the source code and modify it to your needs. We'd also be happy to include your improvements into CryFS directly.
        p
          a.btn.btn-default href="#" role="button" View details »

